commandDescription: Executes one or more lines of anonymous Apex code entered on the command line, or executes the code in a local file.
apexCodeFileDescription: Path to a local file that contains Apex code.
targetUsernameDescription: A username or alias for the target org. Overrides the default target org.
logLevelDescription: logging level for this command invocation.
logLevelLongDescription: Permissible values are: trace, debug, info, warn, error, fatal, TRACE, DEBUG, INFO, WARN, ERROR, FATAL
